{"tid":878428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國安顧問John Bolton警告：中國導彈直指「俄國心臟」","createTime":"2018-10-27T06:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T00:19:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"46c054bd33e6cf5566f5de95efd043d196142b70","tid":878428,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpx1kOnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpx1kOnG.jpg&h=7bd2835c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國家安全顧問波頓（John Bolton）昨日訪問喬治亞首都特比利西（Tbilisi）時表示，針對中國的挑釁行為，美國想要與俄羅斯進行戰略對話，同時也警告俄羅斯，中國的導彈已經對莫斯科構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透報導，美國國家安全顧問波頓表示，中國的飛彈能力對俄國構成威脅，尤其是莫斯科，「俄國心臟地帶」就在中國飛彈的攻擊距離內。波頓也說，美國計劃退出的「中程飛彈條約」（INF）是「冷戰的遺留物」。<br />\n<br />\n波頓還表示，如果俄國離開克里米亞半島和烏克蘭的唐貝斯（Donbass），停止在西方國家使用非法化學武器暗殺俄國流亡人士，以及減少對中東的侵擾，將會很有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2593683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2593683&d=ohugl7sx8BWB9kVPH%2BgyFAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=08d79568\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2593683&h=1a2271aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2593683</a>"},{"pid":"833009afa66830665239007bf9264f44ae211100","tid":878428,"uid":152476,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"聯俄滅支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831625948eb5b6de62b13e85a8c4571bf0585b5e","tid":878428,"uid":45830,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"普京嬲嬲地一野KO支那"},{"pid":"6cb6b8cb3ba994d803e1176170b133ea303f7636","tid":878428,"uid":120678,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"831625948eb5b6de62b13e85a8c4571bf0585b